pageContext.claim: “We have made tremendous progress with the China Virus, but the Fake News refuses to talk about it this close to the Election. COVID, COVID, COVID is being used by them, in total coordination, in order to change our great early election numbers. Should be an election law violation!”
pageContext.analysis: Trump falsely suggests the media is covering the pandemic to deny him re-election. With deaths soaring after the election, covid-19 remained page one news.
